  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "唐代第一篇短篇小说",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 219,
    "line_end": 219
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_li_jing",
    "speaker_name": "李靖",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "公起义兵，本为天下除暴乱，不欲就大事而以私怨斩壮士乎？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 225,
    "line_end": 225
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "有功的人恃功而骄，往往误事，而存心赎罪之人，小心谨慎，全力以赴，成功的机会反大，那便是所谓",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 232,
    "line_end": 232
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "其实说",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 236,
    "line_end": 236
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "，毕竟还是不忘，只不过郑重声明以后不再计较而已，所以在慰劳他的文书中说：",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 236,
    "line_end": 236
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "功高震主",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 270,
    "line_end": 270
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "又说他：",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 274,
    "line_end": 274
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "所以直到七十九岁老死，并没被皇帝斗倒斗垮。《旧唐书》论二李（卫国公李靖、英国公李绩），赞曰：",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 276,
    "line_end": 276
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "公",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 288,
    "line_end": 288
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "吾",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 288,
    "line_end": 288
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "公具以对。妓诵而去。（按：当时人称",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 308,
    "line_end": 308
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "，实则指侍女，古文中",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 308,
    "line_end": 308
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "有",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 308,
    "line_end": 308
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "公曰：",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 320,
    "line_end": 320
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "曰：",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 322,
    "line_end": 322
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "问其姓，曰：",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 324,
    "line_end": 324
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "问其伯仲之次。曰：",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 326,
    "line_end": 326
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "姓张。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 340,
    "line_end": 340
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "妾亦姓张。合是妹。",
    "tone": "陈述",
