    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 342,
    "line_end": 342
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "张氏遥呼：",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 344,
    "line_end": 344
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "煮者何肉？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 346,
    "line_end": 346
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "羊肉，计已熟矣。",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 346,
    "line_end": 346
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "观李郎之行，贫士也。何以致斯异人？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 350,
    "line_end": 350
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "然则将何之？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 354,
    "line_end": 354
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "将避地太原。",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 354,
    "line_end": 354
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "曰：",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 356,
    "line_end": 356
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "公取酒一斗。既巡，客曰：",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 358,
    "line_end": 358
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "曰：",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 360,
    "line_end": 360
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "又曰：",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 364,
    "line_end": 364
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "曰：",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 366,
    "line_end": 366
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "曰：",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 368,
    "line_end": 368
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
