    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 376,
    "line_end": 376
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "公以告刘，刘益喜，自负。既出，而虬髯曰：",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 390,
    "line_end": 390
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "罢弈而请去。既出，谓虬髯曰：",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 408,
    "line_end": 408
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "因共入京。虬髯曰：",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 410,
    "line_end": 410
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
