  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "若疾少间，三日一至门下中书平章政事",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 1,
    "line_start": 514,
    "line_end": 514
  },
  {
    "speaker": null,
    "speaker_name": null,
    "listener": null,
    "text": "杜甫〈送重表侄王砅评事使南海诗〉：",
